author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: "--assignee on claim/release/start-task/pause-task either aliases --author or yields a recovery hint naming --author and pm update --assignee; spec + contracts + docs updated"
parent: pm-mpbb
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: "claim, release, start-task, pause-task, and close-task now accept hidden --assignee as an alias for lifecycle --author, and SDK action contracts expose the alias metadata."
expected_result: Agents that naturally pass --assignee to lifecycle commands get correct ownership behavior or discover the alias through contracts.
actual_result: "Alias parsing, contracts, and lifecycle integration coverage pass, while create/update item assignee semantics remain unchanged."
